parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cylinder head or head gasket can cause coolant leakage, engine overheating, and engine failure, leading to a loss of vehicle control and potentially causing accidents.

engine overheating
oil mixing with coolant
engine stalling
rough engine idle
poor engine performance
and a strong odor of coolant.

intermittent engine failure

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The mixing of oil and coolant can cause engine damage, leading to engine failure and potentially causing accidents.

engine damage
and a strong odor of coolant.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake issues can cause a loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents.
